Here are some instructions to compile and run the code locally.

Build
====================

To combine the multiple javascript files in src/* into a single bundle (build/main.js) we use rollup.
This package can be installed using npm
```
npm install rollup
```

The javascript bundle is built using
```
rollup -c
```

Test
====================
To run phononwebsite locally, build first and then run
```
npm run build
python -m http.server
```
